pilot-link (0.13.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package.
  * Split the Debian build into runtime, library, development, and
    Python 3 binary packages.
  * Rename the historical Python package from python-pisock to
    python3-pisock and document the Python 3 transition.
  * Add Breaks/Replaces metadata so upgrades from the older monolithic
    pilot-link package to the split package set work cleanly.

 -- Pilot Link Packagers <pilot-link@packages.debian.org>  Mon, 16 Feb 2025 12:00:00 +0000
